column5: Two rooms available in a single family residence in nice neighborhood. Both rooms will share a private bathroom, and have access to kitchen, living room, back yard, and washer/dryer. The room with a single bed is a dedicated guest room. The room with a double bed is where my son stays when he is here. Less than 10 miles from downtown / 7 miles from Zilker / 20 mins from Airport. Easy access to main roads in Southwest Austin.
column8: Two Bedrooms in nice home 8 miles from DT / SW ATX
